.SH EXAMPLES
.sp
\fBNOTE:\fP
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
The repository & cache config files are some of the only directly manipulable
parts of a repository that aren\(aqt versioned or backed up, so be careful when
making changes!
